  "reference_number": "INU0257",
  "remarks": "\nSAD Import Export Company is an involved person within the meaning of the Iran (Sanctions) (Nuclear) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019. SAD Import Export Company is or has been acting on behalf or at the direction of a person who has been involved in a relevant nuclear activity, namely the proliferation or development of nuclear weapons in, or for use in, Iran, or an activity that could lead to the development of nuclear weapons in, or for use in, Iran.",
